    Interface to run queries on Stack Overflow via Google's BigQuery service.

    Interfaccia per eseguire le query sui dati di Stack Overflow per mezzo del servizio BigQuery di Google.

      • runQuerySprint1

        com.google.cloud.bigquery.Job runQuerySprint1(java.lang.String yyyy,
                                              java.lang.String mm,
                                              java.lang.String dd,
                                              java.lang.String[] ptid,
                                              java.lang.String limit)
                                       throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Function able to run the queries necessary to satisfy the request 1, 2 and 3 related to Sprint 1. Based on the acquired parameters, the function able to process them is chosen.

        Funzione in grado di eseguire le query necessarie a soddisfare le richieste 1,2 e 3 relative allo Sprint 1. In base ai parametri acquisiti viene scelta la funzione in grado di processarli.

        Parameters:
        yyyy - Obtained from command-line, is the year used to filter the query results.
        mm - Obtained from command-line, is the month used to filter the query results.
        dd - Obtained from command-line, is the day used to filter the query results.
        ptid - Array containing the post type id used to filter the query results.
        limit - Obtained from command-line, is the limit number for the shown results.
        Returns:
        The job for the query.
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - Raised on timeouts.

      • runQuerySprint2

        com.google.cloud.bigquery.Job runQuerySprint2(java.lang.String user,
                                              java.lang.String limit,
                                              java.lang.String order,
                                              java.lang.String where,
                                              java.lang.String nnull,
                                              java.lang.String groupby,
                                              java.lang.String column3)
                                       throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Function able to run the queries necessary to satisfy the request 2, 3, 5 and 6 related to Sprint 2. Based on the acquired parameters, the function able to process them is chosen.

        Funzione in grado di eseguire le query necessarie a soddisfare le richieste 2, 3, 5 e 6 relative allo Sprint 2. In base ai parametri acquisiti viene scelta la funzione in grado di processarli.

        Parameters:
        user - Obtained from command-line, is the user id used to filter the query results.
        limit - Obtained from command-line, is the limit number for the shown results.
        order - Part of the sql code, used to sort the results basing on the specified field.
        where - Part of the sql code, used to filter the query results basing on the user request.
        nnull - Part of the sql code, used to filter the query results basing on the user request.
        groupby - Optional part of the sql code used to group the table results, empty if not needed.
        column3 - Optional part of the sql code indicating the third column of the result table, empty if not needed.
        Returns:
        The job for the query.
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - Raised on timeouts.

      • getResults

        java.util.List<java.lang.Long[]> getResults(com.google.cloud.bigquery.Job job,
                                            java.lang.String query)
                                     throws com.google.cloud.bigquery.JobException,
                                            java.lang.InterruptedException
        Returns the results from the query job.

        Restituisce i valori dei risultati ottenuti tramite la query.

        Parameters:
        job - The job associated to the query.
        query - Index used to identify which query has been used.
        Returns:
        Results as a list of arrays.
        Throws:
        com.google.cloud.bigquery.JobException - Generic error occurred.
        java.lang.InterruptedException - Raised on timeouts.
